{"data":[{"date":"02:11 18/06","title":"HLV Joachim Low: \"\u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/hlv-joachim-low-dt-duc-se-khong-thay-doi-loi-choi.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Joachim Low kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ec3 thua Mexico trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/17/Duc-0-1-Mexico.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nB\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 s\u1edf h\u1eefu d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0ng \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Mexico. Hirving Lozano ghi b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Mannschaft. \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c sau \u0111\u00f3 d\u00f9 d\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh l\u00ean cao nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n khi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Mexico rung l\u00ean.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Joachim Low khang dinh DT Duc se khong thay doi loi choi du de thua Mexico.\" title=\"HLV Joachim Low kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua Mexico.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/hlv-joachim-low-dt-duc-se-khong-thay-doi-loi-choi.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Joachim Low kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua Mexico.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nL\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ed7i lo khi h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9ng trong vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng. Ngo\u00e0i ra, h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed1i lo c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c khi ch\u01a1i b\u1ebf t\u1eafc, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat thi\u1ebfu ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c trong nh\u1eefng pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c thua trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n World Cup, k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau tr\u1eadn thua Algeria v\u00e0o n\u0103m 1982.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, HLV Joachim Low kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i: &quot;Trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 nh\u01b0 m\u1ecdi khi. \u0110\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7p hai, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh&quot;.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;\u0110\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng h\u1eb3n l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, \u00fd t\u00f4i l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng b\u1eaft nh\u1ecbp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00e1p l\u1ef1c. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i. \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c c\u1ea7n t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1eabn c\u00f2n hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n (1h00 ng\u00e0y 24/6) v\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c (21h00 ng\u00e0y 27/6).<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/duc-vs-mexico-bang-f-463-188732.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/ket-qua-duc-vs-mexico-bang-f.png\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/duc-vs-mexico-bang-f-463-188732.html\">\u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico (KT): Nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i to\u00e0n t\u1eadp ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span><br />\r\nNh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 trong h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 cup v\u00e0ng khi ph\u01a1i \u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico, \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t xu\u1ed1ng phong \u0111\u1ed9.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"289","checkdouble":"188760"},{"date":"03:09 18/06","title":"S\u00e1t th\u1ee7 Lozano n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi ch\u1ecdc th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/sat-thu-lozano-noi-gi-sau-khi-choc-thung-luoi-dt-duc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Hirving Lozano \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch khi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c.</h2><h2>Hirving Lozano ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch khi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c ngay \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n World Cup 2018, \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a Mexico mong mu\u1ed1n. Tuy nhi\u00ean trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y m\u00e0 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f2n h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Trung M\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf \u1edf b\u1ea3ng F.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lozano DT Mexico\" title=\"Lozano \u0110T Mexico\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/sat-thu-lozano-noi-gi-sau-khi-choc-thung-luoi-dt-duc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Hirving Lozano ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng gi\u00fap \u0110T Mexico \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Hirving Lozano h\u1ed3 h\u1edfi cho hay: &ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Mexico hay kh\u00f4ng. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Mexico s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 t\u00f4i t\u1eebng ghi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 bao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1u m\u01a1 \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup. Vi\u1ec7c ra s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u00f3 th\u1eadt c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 22, Lozano \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Mexico. &lsquo;C\u01a1n \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c&rdquo; \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 29 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o &ldquo;El Tri&rdquo; v\u00e0 ghi 8 b\u00e0n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9, Lozano ra s\u00e2n g\u1ea7n 150 tr\u1eadn cho Pachuca v\u00e0 PSV, ghi 48 b\u00e0n. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 3 n\u0103m, ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y c\u0169ng t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Man United theo \u0111u\u1ed5i, tuy nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 v\u00ec sao cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb b\u1ecf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Hirving Lozano.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Highlight: \u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico (B\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018)<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span></strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/17/Duc-0-1-Mexico.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#222222;mso-fareast-language:KO\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"288","checkdouble":"188761"},{"date":"02:30 18/06","title":"Ivanovic ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c trong ng\u00e0y Serbia gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/ivanovic-pha-ky-luc-trong-ngay-serbia-gianh-chien-thang-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico, HLV Juan Carlos Osorio th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed k\u00edp gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ed1i 17/6.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Juan Carlos Osorio b\u1eadt m\u00ed chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Mexico tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f9ng h\u1eadu c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1eebng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Mexico v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-1 t\u1ea1i Confed Cup 2017 tuy nhi\u00ean \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u chung cu\u1ed9c.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Juan Carlos Osorio DT Mexico\" title=\"HLV Juan Carlos Osorio \u0110T Mexico\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/hlv-mexico-bat-mi-yeu-to-giup-mexico-danh-bai-dt-duc.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Juan Carlos Osorio \u0103n m\u1eebng c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 sau tr\u1eadn&nbsp;\u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi b\u1edfi ch\u00e2n s\u00fat tr\u1ebb Hirving Lozano, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i Mexico \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean c\u01a1n \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup 2018, khi \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n l\u00e0 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u00f9ng h\u1eadu. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, HLV Juan Carlos Osorio c\u1ee7a Mexico t\u00e2m s\u1ef1: &ldquo;Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 th\u00ec \u0110T Mexico \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i hay h\u01a1n trong hi\u1ec7p 1. Sang t\u1edbi hi\u1ec7p 2, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi s\u1ebd d\u00e2ng cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mexico c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ednh t\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Mario Gomez \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tung v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. H\u00f4m qua ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 4 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ph\u00eda tr\u00ean. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch gi\u00fap Mexico su\u00fdt c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay&rdquo;. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fd gi\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c \u0110T Mexico thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 57 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia n\u00f3i th\u00eam: &ldquo;T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd ra s\u00e2n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 kh\u00e1t khao chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng b\u1ea3o h\u1ecd r\u1eb1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ecbu m\u1ecdi s\u1ee9c \u00e9p ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 t\u00f4i, c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. N\u1ebfu th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00f2n thua th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u00f4m nay h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c, Mexico \u0111ang tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. H\u1ecd th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng E nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u01afCV n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd nh\u1ea5t cho ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch l\u00e0 Brazil.<br />\r\n<strong>Video: \u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico (B\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018)</strong><span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span><br />\r\n<img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height: 220px;\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sat-thu-lozano-noi-gi-sau-khi-choc-thung-luoi-dt-duc-421-188761.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/sat-thu-lozano-