qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 World Cup k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp sau khi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u1ec3 thua Mexico.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-duc-vs-mexico-vinh-danh-nhung-nguoi-dan-ong-dung-cam-421-188758.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/du-am-duc-vs-mexico-vinh-danh-nhung-nguoi-dan-ong-dung-cam.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-duc-vs-mexico-vinh-danh-nhung-nguoi-dan-ong-dung-cam-421-188758.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m \u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico: Vinh danh nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng d\u0169ng c\u1ea3m</span><br />\r\nD\u01b0 \u00e2m \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a khu v\u1ef1c CONCACAF. C\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Mexico \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eddi v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n d\u0169ng c\u1ea3m \u0111\u00e1ng noi g\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-duc-01-mexico-421-188757.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-duc-01-mexico.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-duc-01-mexico-421-188757.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico</span><br />\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ea3ng F VCK World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"287","checkdouble":"188762"},{"date":"02:51 18/06","title":"Thua Mexico, Mats Hummels l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/thua-mexico-mats-hummels-ly-giai-viec-hang-thu-dt-duc-choi-te.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Mats Hummels \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch v\u1ec1 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn thua Mexico.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn \u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/17/Duc-0-1-Mexico.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<br />\r\nH\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n World Cup 2018 c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c bi\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh c\u01a1n \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico. Trong khi h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ebf t\u1eafc, d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m thi\u1ebfu ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c th\u00ec h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y bu\u1ed3n khi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 Mexico khu\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ea3o.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thua Mexico, Mats Hummels l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Thua Mexico, Mats Hummels l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/thua-mexico-mats-hummels-ly-giai-viec-hang-thu-dt-duc-choi-te.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Mats Hummels l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 trong tr\u1eadn thua Mexico.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nSau khi nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, Mats Hummels l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico: &quot;Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecdc l\u00f3t c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n t\u00f4i v\u1edbi Jerome Boateng \u1edf ph\u00eda sau. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1eeb v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u y nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Saudi Arabia, ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch cho nh\u1eefng g\u00ec di\u1ec5n ra trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t, Mexico hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;V\u1edbi b\u1ea3y \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00e1m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tham gia t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 s\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n&quot; - Hummels nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t: &quot;Nh\u01b0ng nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i v\u1eabn hay n\u00f3i, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng c\u00f3 qu\u1ea3 ng\u1ecdt. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ee9c t\u1ec9nh qu\u00e1 mu\u1ed9n. \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c c\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng hai tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i&quot;.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y tung ra \u0111\u1ebfn 25 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong ba \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Argentina (27, 1-1 vs Iceland) v\u00e0 Peru (17, 0-1 vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch).<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1eabn c\u00f2n hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n (1h00 ng\u00e0y 24/6) v\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c (21h00 ng\u00e0y 27/6).<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/duc-vs-mexico-bang-f-463-188732.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/ket-qua-duc-vs-mexico-bang-f.png\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/duc-vs-mexico-bang-f-463-188732.html\">\u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico (KT): Nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i to\u00e0n t\u1eadp ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span><br />\r\nNh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 trong h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 cup v\u00e0ng khi ph\u01a1i \u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico, \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t xu\u1ed1ng phong \u0111\u1ed9.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"286","checkdouble":"188763"},{"date":"03:00 18/06","title":"T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Brazil 1-1 Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 (B\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/tong-hop-brazil-11-thuy-sy-bang-e-world-cup-2018.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft bao nhi\u00eau c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0103n b\u00e0n song r\u1ed1t c\u1ee5c c\u00e1c v\u0169 c\u00f4ng Samba ch\u1ec9 thu v\u1ec1 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.</h2><strong>B\u1ea2N QUY\u1ec0N VTV</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH THI \u0110\u1ea4U<br>\r\nBrazil: </strong>Alisson, Danilo, Thiago Silva, Miranda, Marcelo (c), Paulinho, Casemiro, Coutinho, Willian, Gabriel Jesus, Neymar.<br>\r\n<strong>Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9: </strong>Yann Sommer, Stephan Lichtsteiner (c), Fabian  Schar, Manuel Akanji, Ricardo Rodriguez, Valon Behrami, Granit Xhaka,  Xherdan Shaqiri, Blerim Dzemaili, Steven Zuber, Haris Seferovic.<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"285","checkdouble":"188764"},{"date":"03:32 18/06","title":"HLV Carlos Osorio b\u1eadt m\u00ed y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 gi\u00fap Mexico \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/hlv-mexico-bat-mi-yeu-to-giup-mexico-danh-bai-dt-duc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico, HLV Juan Carlos Osorio th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed k\u00edp gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ed1i 17/6.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Juan Carlos Osorio b\u1eadt m\u00ed chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Mexico tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f9ng h\u1eadu c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1eebng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Mexico v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-1 t\u1ea1i Confed Cup 2017 tuy nhi\u00ean \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u chung cu\u1ed9c.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Juan Carlos Osorio DT Mexico\" title=\"HLV Juan Carlos Osorio \u0110T Mexico\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/hlv-mexico-bat-mi-yeu-to-giup-mexico-danh-bai-dt-duc.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Juan Carlos Osorio \u0103n m\u1eebng c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 sau tr\u1eadn&nbsp;\u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi b\u1edfi ch\u00e2n s\u00fat tr\u1ebb Hirving Lozano, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i Mexico \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean c\u01a1n \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup 2018, khi \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n l\u00e0 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u00f9ng h\u1eadu. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, HLV Juan Carlos Osorio c\u1ee7a Mexico t\u00e2m s\u1ef1: &ldquo;Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 th\u00ec \u0110T Mexico \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i hay h\u01a1n trong hi\u1ec7p 1. Sang t\u1edbi hi\u1ec7p 2, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi s\u1ebd d\u00e2ng cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mexico c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ednh t\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Mario Gomez \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tung v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. H\u00f4m qua ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 4 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ph\u00eda tr\u00ean. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch gi\u00fap Mexico su\u00fdt c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay&rdquo;. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fd gi\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c \u0110T Mexico thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 57 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia n\u00f3i th\u00eam: &ldquo;T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd ra s\u00e2n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 kh\u00e1t khao chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng b\u1ea3o h\u1ecd r\u1eb1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ecbu m\u1ecdi s\u1ee9c \u00e9p ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 t\u00f4i, c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. N\u1ebfu th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00f2n thua th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u00f4m nay h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c, Mexico \u0111ang tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. H\u1ecd th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng E nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u01afCV n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd nh\u1ea5t cho ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch l\u00e0 Brazil.<br />\r\n<strong>Video: \u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico (B\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018)</strong><span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span><br />\r\n<img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height: 220px;\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sat-thu-lozano-noi-gi-sau-khi-choc-thung-luoi-dt-duc-421-188761.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/sat-thu-lozano-noi-gi-sau-khi-choc-thung-luoi-dt-duc.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sat-thu-lozano-noi-gi-sau-khi-choc-thung-luoi-dt-duc-421-188761.html\">S\u00e1t th\u1ee7 Lozano n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi ch\u1ecdc th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c?</span><br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Hirving Lozano \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch khi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/thua-mexico-mats-hummels-ly-giai-viec-hang-thu-dt-duc-choi-te-465-188763.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/thua-mexico-mats-hummels-ly-giai-viec-hang-thu-dt-duc-choi-te.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/thua-mexico-mats-hummels-ly-giai-viec-hang-thu-dt-duc-choi-te-465-188763.html\">Thua Mexico, Mats Hummels l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7</span><br />\r\nMats Hummels \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch v\u1ec1 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn thua Mexico.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/thua-mexico-dt-duc-vuong-loi-nguyen-nha-vo-dich-tai-world-cup-465-188759.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/thua-mexico-dt-duc-vuong-loi-nguyen-nha-vo-dich-tai-world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/thua-mexico-dt-duc-vuong-loi-nguyen-nha-vo-dich-tai-world-cup-465-188759.html\">Thua Mexico, \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c v\u01b0\u1edbng l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch t\u1ea1i World Cup</span><br />\r\n\u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ee9 ba li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 World Cup k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp sau khi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u1ec3 thua Mexico.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-duc-vs-mexico-vinh-danh-nhung-nguoi-dan-ong-dung-cam-421-188758.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/du-am-duc-vs-mexico-vinh-danh-nhung-nguoi-dan-ong-dung-cam.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-duc-vs-mexico-vinh-danh-nhung-nguoi-dan-ong-dung-cam-421-188758.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m \u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico: Vinh danh nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng d\u0169ng c\u1ea3m</span><br />\r\nD\u01b0 \u00e2m \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a khu v\u1ef1c CONCACAF. C\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Mexico \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eddi v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n d\u0169ng c\u1ea3m \u0111\u00e1ng noi g\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-duc-01-mexico-421-188757.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-duc-01-mexico.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-duc-01-mexico-421-188757.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico</span><br />\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ea3ng F VCK World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"284","checkdouble":"188768"},{"date":"03:17 18/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 1-1 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-brazil-11-thuy-si.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 1-1 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ea3ng E VCK World Cup 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n- 12 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch v\u1eeba qua ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t, Brazil th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi 10 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Neymar \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i t\u1edbi 10 l\u1ea7n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 1-1 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n Neymar t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i World Cup l\u00e0 Alan Shearer c\u1ee7a Anh n\u0103m 1998 (11 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 1-1 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 1-1 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/Zuber-danh-dau-tung-luoi-Brazil.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Zuber \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 1-1 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n- Steven Zuber \u0111\u00e3 tham gia tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o 6 b\u00e0n sau 6 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t cho Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 (4 b\u00e0n, 2 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- T\u00ednh c\u1ea3 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Philippe Coutinho tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y S\u0129, Brazil \u0111\u00e3 ghi 37 b\u00e0n t\u1eeb ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m t\u1ea1i World Cup t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1966 t\u1edbi nay, \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 11 h\u01a1n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- C\u1ea3 2 l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a Brazil v\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 t\u1ea1i World Cup \u0111\u1ec1u k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a (tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 2-2 n\u0103m 1950).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Brazil c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 13 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup, th\u1eafng 10 (h\u00f2a 3) k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1998 t\u1edbi nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- \u0110\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 3 sau 19 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup m\u00e0 Brazil kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng (h\u00f2a 3) t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1934 t\u1edbi nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 kh\u00f4ng thua tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n t\u1ea1i World Cup trong c\u1ea3 3 k\u1ef3 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tham d\u1ef1 (th\u1eafng 2, h\u00f2a 1).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Xherdan Shaqiri \u0111\u00e3 tham gia tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o 6 trong s\u1ed1 7 b\u00e0n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn (4 b\u00e0n, 2 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Brazil 1-1 Thuy Sy\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 1-1 Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/Thong-so-Brazil.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 1-1 Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn Brazil 1-1 Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 (B\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018):</strong>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/18/Brazil-1-1-Thuy-Sy.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 1-1 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-bong-da-brazil-vs-thuy-si-bang-e-421-188756.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Brazil vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/brazil-vs-thuy-si-bang-e-463-188745.html\">Brazil 1-1 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 (KT): D\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed3i, Selecao \u0111\u00e0nh ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chia \u0111i\u1ec3m</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"283","checkdouble":"188769"},{"date":"06:01 18/06","title":"Sau v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018: H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, HAGL \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t ng\u00e3 ng\u1ef1a","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/sau-vong-14-vleague-2018-ha-noi-hagl-dong-loat-nga-ngua.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng c\u00fa s\u1ed1c khi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ch\u1ecbu thua \u0111\u1ed9i \u00e1p ch\u00f3t tr\u00ean BXH l\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC c\u00f2n HAGL ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 ng\u1ef1a tr\u00ean s\u00e2n SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng. N\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y V-League lu\u00f4n ch\u1ee9a \u0111\u1ef1ng nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc.\r\n\r\n</h2><br />\r\n<h2>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i thua s\u1ed1c S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC</h2>\r\n<h2><o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong c\u01a1n m\u01b0a n\u1eb7ng h\u1ea1t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t chu\u1ed7i 13 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1eb7ng 2-5 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u1edf v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018. \u0110\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 c\u00fa s\u1ed1c r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn khi m\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Oseni. Tuy nhi\u00ean sau \u0111\u00f3 \u2018h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\u2019 Qu\u1ed1c Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a cho S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i th\u1ebf c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sau v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, HAGL \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t ng\u00e3 ng\u1ef1a h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sau v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, HAGL \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t ng\u00e3 ng\u1ef1a h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/Sau-vong-14-V-League-2018-Ha-Noi,-HAGL-dong-loat-nga-ngua-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i h\u1ebft b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u1edf v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n, ngo\u1ea1i binh Da Sylva \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp h\u1eb3n m\u1ed9t c\u00fa poker b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 5-2 chung cu\u1ed9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t th\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 n\u00e0y gi\u00fap S\u00e0i G\u00f2n t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi an to\u00e0n khi \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf xa \u0111\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft v\u1eabn \u0111ang gi\u1eef c\u1ef1 ly an to\u00e0n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh, tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n r\u00fat ra nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1edbm v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch t\u1ea1i V-League 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>HAGL nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eebng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi m\u1ea1ch 9 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng \u00edt ai ng\u1edd trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh v\u00e0 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam, t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 HAGL s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i khi m\u00e0 h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf tr\u00ean s\u00e2n H\u00f2a Xu\u00e2n chi\u1ec1u 17/6 m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa cho th\u1ea5y HAGL v\u1eabn c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"SHB Da Nang vs HAGL\" title=\"SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/dsc_0341-2030.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i HAGL tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. \u1ea2nh: Bongda.com.vn</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 thi \u0111\u1ea5u thi\u1ebfu ch\u1ea5t th\u00e9p, tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa m\u1ecfng c\u00f2n h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng v\u1eabn b\u1ecf ph\u00ed nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7, \u201cG\u1ed7\u201d ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u00eam th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i V-League 2018. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u2018h\u1ed3i chu\u00f4ng c\u1ea3nh t\u1ec9nh\u2019 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. N\u1ebfu c\u1ee9 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ec7 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, HAGL kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 5 tr\u00ean BXH nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/17/Highlight-Da-Nang-vs-HAGL-.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<h2>N\u00f3ng cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3 SLNA v\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u00f9ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 k\u00e9o TP.HCM xu\u1ed1ng cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng. T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Miura \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng. Thua 0-2 chung cu\u1ed9c, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng \u00e1p ch\u00f3t tr\u00ean BXH v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0u tham v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u1edf 12 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, TP.HCM ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn play-off ho\u1eb7c x\u1ea5u h\u01a1n l\u00e0 m\u1ea5t quy\u1ec1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i V-League 2019.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi m\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf V-League n\u0103m nay th\u00ec cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh cho nh\u1eefng su\u1ea5t tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, c\u1ea3 SLNA, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC, TP.HCM v\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec1u \u2018\u0111\u1ea1t ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n\u2019 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, h\u1ecd ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1eaft chiu c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i qua t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh su\u1ea5t r\u1edbt h\u1ea1ng \u1edf cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br />\r\nXem th\u00eam: <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague/ket-qua-25.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, LT\u0110, BXH V-League 2018</span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/vleague/hlv-minh-phuong-that-vong-vi-hagl-bat-dau-da-tieu-xao-291-188742.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-minh-phuong-that-vong-vi-hagl-bat-dau-da-tieu-xao.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/vleague/hlv-minh-phuong-that-vong-vi-hagl-bat-dau-da-tieu-xao-291-188742.html\">HLV Minh Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00ec HAGL b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec3u x\u1ea3o</span><br />\r\nGi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng HLV Minh Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 vui m\u1eebng, thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a HAGL b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u nhi\u1ec5m nh\u1eefng t\u1eadt x\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a V-League.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-thua-nhan-diem-yeu-sau-tran-thua-shb-da-nang-168-188740.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-hagl-thua-nhan-diem-yeu-sau-tran-thua-shb-da-nang.png\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-thua-nhan-diem-yeu-sau-tran-thua-shb-da-nang-168-188740.html\">HLV HAGL th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu sau tr\u1eadn thua SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng</span><br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh c\u1ee7a HAGL \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn HAGL ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 14 V-League.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/vleague/hlv-chu-dinh-nghiem-phu-nhan-viec-ha-noi-thua-dam-vi-world-cup-2018-291-188754.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-chu-dinh-nghiem-phu-nhan-viec-ha-noi-thua-dam-vi-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/vleague/hlv-chu-dinh-nghiem-phu-nhan-viec-ha-noi-thua-dam-vi-world-cup-2018-291-188754.html\">HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i thua \u0111\u1eadm v\u00ec World Cup 2018</span><br />\r\nHLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i thua \u0111\u1eadm c\u00f3 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb World Cup 2018, \u00f4ng cho r\u1eb1ng ch\u00ednh kh\u00e1t khao c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</span></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"282","checkdouble":"188775"},{"date":"07:01 18/06","title":"HLV Tite t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn v\u00ec \u0110T Brazil kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf d\u1eabn b\u00e0n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/hlv-tite-tuc-gian-vi-dt-brazil-khong-tan-dung-duoc-loi-the-dan-ban.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Tite t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn v\u00ec \u0110T Brazil qu\u00e1 ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p trong nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf d\u1eabn b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ebft li\u1ec5u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn Brazil 1-1 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/18/Brazil-1-1-Thuy-Sy.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110T Brazil h\u00f2a \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n, \u0110T Brazil ch\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t 20 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m s\u00fat xa c\u1ee7a Philippe Coutinho. Sau \u0111\u00f3, \u0110T Brazil c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u00e0m b\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, trong khi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 t\u1eeb t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Zuber.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Tite tuc gian vi DT Brazil khong tan dung duoc loi the dan ban.\" title=\"HLV Tite t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn v\u00ec \u0110T Brazil kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf d\u1eabn b\u00e0n.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/hlv-tite-tuc-gian-vi-dt-brazil-khong-tan-dung-duoc-loi-the-dan-ban.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Tite t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn v\u00ec \u0110T Brazil kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf d\u1eabn b\u00e0n.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn khi b\u1ecb g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a, Selecao d\u1ed3n l\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a \u0110T Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 rung l\u00ean l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. Nh\u1eefng m\u0169i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Brazil tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y nh\u01b0 Neymar, Gabriel Jesus hay Willian \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Brazil tung ra \u0111\u1ebfn 21 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 b\u1eb1ng 6 l\u1ea7n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn Selecao n\u1eb1m trong nh\u00f3m nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Argentina (27 l\u1ea7n, 1-1 Iceland), \u0110\u1ee9c (25, 0-1 Mexico) v\u00e0 Peru (17, 0-1 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Tite t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn v\u00ec \u0110T Brazil<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;T\u00f4i mong \u0111\u1ee3i m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00ean k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y d\u0129 nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c&quot; - HLV Tite chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u: &quot;\u1ede giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a World Cup, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf d\u1eabn b\u00e0n, ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m. B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nhanh h\u01a1n&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn \u0110T Brazil ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 hai \u1edf b\u1ea3ng E khi Serbia \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Costa Rica v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1-0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. Selecao v\u1eabn c\u00f2n hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eb7p Costa Rica (19h00 ng\u00e0y 22/6) v\u00e0 Serbia (1h00 ng\u00e0y 28/6).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/brazil-vs-thuy-si-bang-e-463-188745.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/ket-qua-bong-da-brazil-vs-thuy-si-bang-e.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/brazil-vs-thuy-si-bang-e-463-188745.html\">Brazil 1-1 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 (KT): D\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed3i, Selecao \u0111\u00e0nh ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chia \u0111i\u1ec3m</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft bao nhi\u00eau c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0103n b\u00e0n song r\u1ed1t c\u1ee5c c\u00e1c v\u0169 c\u00f4ng Samba ch\u1ec9 thu v\u1ec1 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"281","checkdouble":"188778"},{"date":"06:46 18/06","title":"FIFA m\u1eafc s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1ec1 t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/18/fifa-mac-su-co-hai-huoc-ve-ty-so-tran-duc-vs-mexico.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ngay gi\u00e2y th\u1ee9 19 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico thu\u1ed9c b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 t\u1ed1i qua, FIFA \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea1m sai l\u1ea7m h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc khi ghi sai t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">C\u00f3 l\u1ebd v\u00ec l\u1ed7i k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt ho\u1eb7c l\u00fd do n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea3ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u00ean truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a hai k\u00eanh ZDF v\u00e0 ARD (\u0110\u1ee9c) t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n World Cup 2018 c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 World Cup b\u1ecb hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb sai. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, v\u00e0o gi\u00e2y 19 hi\u1ec7p 1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-0 nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 cho \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, d\u00f9 t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 th\u1ef1c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Luzhniki l\u00fac \u0111\u00f3 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 0-0.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"FIFA m\u1eafc s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1ec1 t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"FIFA m\u1eafc s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1ec1 t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/5w993qhighc0bild.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">FIFA m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m trong kh\u00e2u k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt khi truy\u1ec1n t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 cho hai k\u00eanh truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh \u0110\u1ee9c. H\u1ecd in sai t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ngay \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn. \u1ea2nh: Bild.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u0129 nhi\u00ean, s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 n\u00f3i tr\u00ean d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi nh\u1eadn b\u1edfi h\u00e0ng tri\u1ec7u fan tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111ang d\u00f5i theo \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hai k\u00eanh ZDF v\u00e0 ARD thu t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1eeb FIFA. Ngo\u00e0i ra, m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed3 h\u1ecda hay b\u1ea3ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec1u do Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ph\u1ee5 tr\u00e1ch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDo \u0111\u00f3, FIFA ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m cho s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i. Nh\u1ea7m l\u1eabn tr\u00ean ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5 sau \u0111\u00f3 h\u01a1n ch\u1ee5c gi\u00e2y. V\u1edbi tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c, h\u1ecd tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00eam \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng khi g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 0-1 trong 90 ph\u00fat. Mexico thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t hay v\u00e0 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a HLV Joachim Loew \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh, ch\u01a1i th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00f4 h\u1ed3n. \u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00f9ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ea5y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede ph\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, b\u00e1o Bild gi\u1eadt t\u00edt: \"S\u1ef1 s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi lo s\u1ee3 v\u1ec1 World Cup\". C\u00f2n b\u00e1o Kicker b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00f4m nay xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t \u1ed5n. V\u00e0 Mexico, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu \u1edf c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 World Cup, \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. B\u00e1o Kicker vi\u1ebft: \"Tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u World Cup theo c\u00e1ch r\u1ea5t l\u1ed9n x\u1ed9n: Lozano tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh y\u1ebfu \u0111u\u1ed1i\".<br>\r\n<h2>C\u00e1c tin b\u00e0i kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-mexico-bat-mi-yeu-to-giup-mexico-danh-bai-dt-duc-421-188768.html\">HLV Carlos Osorio b\u1eadt m\u00ed y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 gi\u00fap Mexico \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/thua-mexico-mats-hummels-ly-giai-viec-hang-thu-dt-duc-choi-te-465-188763.html\">Thua Mexico, Mats Hummels l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sat-thu-lozano-noi-gi-sau-khi-choc-thung-luoi-dt-duc-421-188761.html\">S\u00e1t th\u1ee7 Lozano n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi ch\u1ecdc th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-joachim-low-dt-duc-se-khong-thay-doi-loi-choi-465-188760.html\">HLV Joachim Low: \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/thua-mexico-dt-duc-vuong-loi-nguyen-nha-vo-dich-tai-world-cup-465-188759.html\">Thua Mexico, \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c v\u01b0\u1edbng l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch t\u1ea1i World Cup</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-duc-vs-mexico-vinh-danh-nhung-nguoi-dan-ong-dung-cam-421-188758.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m \u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico: Vinh danh nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng d\u0169ng c\u1ea3m</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"280","checkdouble":"188779"},{"date":"17:56 17/06","title":"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/ket-qua-da-nang-vs-hagl-vong-14-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 14 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2018 h\u00f4m nay. Th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n, di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn ch\u00ednh, video b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, clip highlights tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL Ho\u00e0ng Anh Gia Lai v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018 17h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 17/6.</h2>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 hi\u1ec7p 1: \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL: 0-1<br />\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n: Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng (8')<br />\r\n<hr />\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/17/171152-Da-Nang-vs-HAGL-09.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">HAGL v\u00e0 \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018 v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 3 ngo\u1ea1i binh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u00e0n l\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 uy hi\u1ebfp khung th\u00e0nh HAGL.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng pha b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c g\u00e2y s\u1ee9c \u00e9p l\u00ean khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai. Ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 2, \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0103n b\u00e0n khi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e2u b\u1ed5ng v\u00e0o khu v\u1ef1c 16m50 c\u1ee7a HAGL v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1edbp th\u1eddi c\u01a1 tung ra c\u00fa s\u00fat \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly g\u1ea7n song th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c ngay sau \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n HAGL&nbsp;c\u0169ng rung chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111i tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch. Sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng h\u00fat ch\u1ebft \u0111\u00f3, HAGL \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c h\u1ecd c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u1edf kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch 25m so v\u1edbi khung th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t th\u1ea7n s\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng \u0111i cu\u1ed9n v\u00e0o g\u00f3c xa khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh V\u0103n H\u01b0ng b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c nh\u00ecn b\u00f3ng \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha \u0103n mi\u1ebfng, tr\u1ea3 mi\u1ebfng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb hai \u0111\u1ed9i. \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng \u00e1p \u0111\u1eb7t s\u1ee9c \u00e9p r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh v\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n HAGL nh\u01b0ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p \u0103n \u00fd h\u01a1n, HAGL c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng song h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, qua \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi l\u00e0 1-0 nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"279","checkdouble":"188724"},{"date":"16:01 17/06","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i 19h00 ng\u00e0y 17/6 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-vong-14-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00f2ng 14 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018 l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 17/6.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00f2ng 14 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018 l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 17/6.</h2>\r\nKh\u00f4ng xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, vui l\u00f2ng click t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-vong-14-vleague-2018-372-188725.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP S\u00c0I G\u00d2N VS H\u00c0 N\u1ed8I</strong></u></span></span><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"278","checkdouble":"188725"},{"date":"16:53 17/06","title":"Sergio Ramos khi\u1ebfn Conte kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real Madrid?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/19/sergio-ramos-khien-conte-khong-the-dan-dat-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Luka Modric l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111e d\u1ecda Argentina \u2013 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nModric g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1edbi Argentina<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Croatia d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u Phi Nigeria v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0, Argentina \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 khi ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Iceland. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng b\u0103ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y, Croatia t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D &ndash; b\u1ea3ng t\u1eed th\u1ea7n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Argentina m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh Croatia \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, Luka Modric c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1nh l\u1edbn. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i cho Real Madrid cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Argentina r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, nh\u01b0ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n. Hy v\u1ecdng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi h\u1ecd.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Modric l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111e d\u1ecda Argentina sau khi gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean\" title=\"B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Modric Croatia vs Nigeria\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/modric.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Modric l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111e d\u1ecda Argentina sau khi gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd, Argentina \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau th\u00edch nh\u1ea5t \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u0103ng s\u1ee9c \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Nigeria, Luka Modric \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi = anh ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, h\u01a1n n\u1eefa c\u00f2n ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. Modric cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i. C\u1ea3m \u01a1n Ch\u00faa v\u00ec t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n, th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n s\u1ecdc ca-ro \u0111ang c\u00f3 ch\u00fat \u00edt l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D. \u1ede 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, Croatia s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi Argentina v\u00e0 Iceland, v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi Modric \u0111e d\u1ecda Argentina, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd anh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/argentina-ra-quan-that-vong-va-bai-hoc-ve-su-hieu-qua-421-188678.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/argentina-ra-quan-that-vong-va-bai-hoc-ve-su-hieu-qua.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/argentina-ra-quan-that-vong-va-bai-hoc-ve-su-hieu-qua-421-188678.html\">Argentina ra qu\u00e2n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3</span><br>\r\nD\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t &ndash; Argentina. C\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t &ndash; Argentina. Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng &ndash; v\u1eabn l\u00e0 Argentina. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ra qu\u00e2n, Argentina g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-croatia-vs-nigeria-bang-d-world-cup-2018-hiep-1-461-188676.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/tong-hop-croatia-vs-nigeria-bang-d-world-cup-2018-hiep-1.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-croatia-vs-nigeria-bang-d-world-cup-2018-hiep-1-461-188676.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Croatia 2-0 Nigeria (B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nH\u01a1n h\u1eb3n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u, Croatia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"277","checkdouble":"188726"},{"date":"17:10 17/06","title":"\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Harry Kane n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/12/doi-truong-harry-kane-noi-gi-truoc-tran-ra-quan-cua-dt-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Harry Kane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Tottenham kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd \u0111\u1eb7t l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0110TQG l\u00ean tr\u00ean m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Harry Kane \u0111\u1eb7t l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh l\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHarry Kane \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 ghi 30 b\u00e0n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Tottenham \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 trong danh s\u00e1ch Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi, k\u00e9m ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u Salah 2 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Harry Kane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Harry Kane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/12/doi-truong-harry-kane-noi-gi-truoc-tran-ra-quan-cua-dt-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kane \u0111\u1eb7t l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh l\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, gi\u00fap Anh gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn Nga. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n Kane \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Southgate tin t\u01b0\u1edfng trao cho chi\u1ebfc b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/harry-kane-dat-muc-tieu-khong-tuong-tai-world-cup-421-188300.html\" target=\"_blank\">Harry Kane quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f9ng Anh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch\u00a0World Cup 2018</span>, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHarry Kane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Tottenham kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd \u0111\u1eb7t l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0110TQG l\u00ean tr\u00ean m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1eb7t l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0110TQG l\u00ean l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 gi\u00fap Anh gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y vinh d\u1ef1 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111eo chi\u1ebfc b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1eeb NHM. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u01a1i quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng trong t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Harry Kane quy\u1ebft gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n \u1edf b\u1ea3ng G g\u1eb7p Tunisia, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 y\u1ebfu h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, Harry Kane kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Tam s\u01b0 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi tuyen Anh vo dich World Cup 2018 voi cau thu Tottenham?\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Tottenham?\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/11/doi-tuyen-anh-khong-the-vo-dich-world-cup-voi-cau-thu-tottenham.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kane mu\u1ed1n \u0110T Anh gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t, qua \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1o t\u00e2m l\u00fd thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. Tunisia kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng y\u1ebfu, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng h\u1ecd. Anh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00fang s\u1ee9c v\u00e0 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cTo\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Tunisia, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"276","checkdouble":"188730"},{"date":"17:10 17/06","title":"Modric: \"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Argentina ph\u1ea3i run s\u1ee3\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/11/modric-chung-toi-da-khien-argentina-phai-run-so.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Luka Modric l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111e d\u1ecda Argentina \u2013 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nModric g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1edbi Argentina<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Croatia d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u Phi Nigeria v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0, Argentina \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 khi ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Iceland. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng b\u0103ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y, Croatia t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D &ndash; b\u1ea3ng t\u1eed th\u1ea7n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Argentina m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh Croatia \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, Luka Modric c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1nh l\u1edbn. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i cho Real Madrid cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Argentina r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, nh\u01b0ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n. Hy v\u1ecdng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi h\u1ecd.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Modric l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111e d\u1ecda Argentina sau khi gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean\" title=\"B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Modric Croatia vs Nigeria\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/modric.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Modric l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111e d\u1ecda Argentina sau khi gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd, Argentina \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau th\u00edch nh\u1ea5t \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u0103ng s\u1ee9c \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Nigeria, Luka Modric \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi = anh ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, h\u01a1n n\u1eefa c\u00f2n ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. Modric cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i. C\u1ea3m \u01a1n Ch\u00faa v\u00ec t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n, th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n s\u1ecdc ca-ro \u0111ang c\u00f3 ch\u00fat \u00edt l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D. \u1ede 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, Croatia s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi Argentina v\u00e0 Iceland, v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi Modric \u0111e d\u1ecda Argentina, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd anh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/argentina-ra-quan-that-vong-va-bai-hoc-ve-su-hieu-qua-421-188678.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/argentina-ra-quan-that-vong-va-bai-hoc-ve-su-hieu-qua.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/argentina-ra-quan-that-vong-va-bai-hoc-ve-su-hieu-qua-421-188678.html\">Argentina ra qu\u00e2n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3</span><br>\r\nD\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t &ndash; Argentina. C\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t &ndash; Argentina. Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng &ndash; v\u1eabn l\u00e0 Argentina. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ra qu\u00e2n, Argentina g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-croatia-vs-nigeria-bang-d-world-cup-2018-hiep-1-461-188676.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/tong-hop-croatia-vs-nigeria-bang-d-world-cup-2018-hiep-1.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-croatia-vs-nigeria-bang-d-world-cup-2018-hiep-1-461-188676.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Croatia 2-0 Nigeria (B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nH\u01a1n h\u1eb3n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u, Croatia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"275","checkdouble":"188731"}]}